						               													<description>&amp;quot;Chameleon - the game where you can run and you CAN hide!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Chameleon is a new and exciting board game that is a combination of Chess, Draughts, Chinese Checkers and Backgammon. It is a game of tactics, cunning and ambush.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Plan your attack, secure your defence, strike when ready.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Chameleon is played on 6 colour game board and comes with 12 pegs, 2 'chameleon' die, a rules booklet and a strategy brochure. Each player (either black or white) plays with 6 pegs that are red, yellow, green, blue, orange and purple.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The aim of the game is to be the first player to move all six tokens from your 'starting grid' into your 'home base' whilst trying to stop (or zap!) your opponent from doing the same. If you're on your own colour you are a chameleon and can't be seen. If you're off your colour you'd better watch out!&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
